watching us live on Facebook

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:15.400
and YouTube [applause].

00:04:18.340 --> 00:04:22.800
So let's give a big Washington,
DC, McLean, Virginia,

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:26.510
welcome to the Calverton School
