00:04:26.510 --> 00:04:30.640
[ Applause ]

00:04:30.640 --> 00:04:35.510
The Tinmouth Elementary
School in Tinmouth, Vermont.

00:04:35.510 --> 00:04:39.160
[ Applause ]

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:42.440
And the John Dawes
School in Englishtown,

00:04:42.440 --> 00:04:45.620
New Jersey [applause].

00:04:45.620 --> 00:04:48.600
So welcome, all of you.

